## Keyword Performance Benchmarks

### Current State (From Search Console)

Based on analysis of Search Console data:

| Metric | Current | Target (3 months) | Target (6 months) |
|--------|---------|-------------------|-------------------|
| Average Position (brand) | 5.2 | 3.0 | 2.0 |
| Average Position (commercial) | 12.4 | 8.0 | 5.0 |
| CTR (position 1-3) | 18% | 25% | 30% |
| CTR (position 4-10) | 4% | 8% | 12% |

### CTR Optimization Targets

Position-based CTR benchmarks (industry average vs. target):

| Position | Industry Avg | Our Target |
|----------|--------------|------------|
| 1 | 28% | 35% |
| 2 | 15% | 20% |
| 3 | 11% | 15% |
| 4-6 | 6% | 10% |
| 7-10 | 3% | 6% |

**CTR improvement tactics**:
- Optimized meta titles with hooks
- Meta descriptions with CTA and differentiators
- FAQ schema for expanded SERP presence
- LocalBusiness schema for local searches

