## Keyword Mapping to Content Sections

### Where Keywords Should Appear

| Location | Primary KW | Secondary KW | Notes |
|----------|------------|--------------|-------|
| H1 | Required | Optional | Natural, not stuffed |
| First paragraph | Required | 1-2 max | Within first 100 words |
| H2 headers | Optional | Optional | Only if natural |
| Body content | 2-3x | 3-5x | Distributed naturally |
| Meta title | Required | Optional | Front-loaded |
| Meta description | Required | 1-2 max | With CTA |
| Alt text | For relevant images | — | Descriptive, not stuffed |
| URL slug | Required | — | Already set (preserve) |

### Keyword Density Guidelines

- **Target density**: 1-2% for primary keyword
- **Maximum density**: 3% (avoid over-optimization)
- **Natural language**: Keywords in flowing sentences, not lists

